---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Base64 Encoder & Decoder
description: Free online Base64 encoder and decoder. Convert text to Base64 and decode Base64 to text instantly. Supports file encoding. No signup required.
keywords: Base64 encoder, Base64 decoder, encode Base64, decode Base64, Base64 converter, text to Base64, Base64 to text, file to Base64
permalink: /tools/base64-encoder/
toolId: base64-encoder
toolJs: base64.js
ogImage: base64-encoder.jpg
---
{# Get tool data from tools.json #}
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<!-- Schema.org BreadcrumbList -->
